sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid specialised participant visuals
accDescr {
Demonstrates specialised Mermaid participant kinds rendered with distinct header icons.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/22-specialised-participant-visuals/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/22-specialised-participant-visuals
}
actor User as Human operator
participant Edge@{"type":"boundary"} as External boundary
participant FlowController@{"type":"control","alias":"FlowController"} as Flow controller
participant OrderEntity@{"type":"entity","alias":"OrderEntity","label":"Order entity"}
participant DB@{"type":"database","alias":"IgnoredInternalDb","name":"Primary store"}
participant CollectionsNode@{"type":"collections","alias":"CollectionsNode","label":"Collections store"}
participant JobQueue@{"type":"queue","alias":"JobQueue","label":"Job queue"}
User->>Edge: Start request [Mermaid: User->>Edge: Start request]
Edge->>FlowController: Route request [Mermaid: Edge->>FlowController: Route request]
FlowController->>OrderEntity: Load aggregate [Mermaid: FlowController->>OrderEntity: Load aggregate]
FlowController->>DB: Read persistence [Mermaid: FlowController->>DB: Read persistence]
FlowController->>CollectionsNode: Gather related rows [Mermaid: FlowController->>CollectionsNode: Gather related rows]
FlowController->>JobQueue: Enqueue follow-up [Mermaid: FlowController->>JobQueue: Enqueue follow-up]
